txt.en: 'Spies have reported that the Ordâkhai in Eshadûr have received a new supply of explosive black powder. We would like you to infiltrate Eshadûr and destroy the explosives before they can be used against us.'
You have destroyed the Ordâkhai's stock of black powder! Return with Khâdamul to report your success.
There is no twist in this mission.
The Dumûri have learned the Ordâkhai in Eshadûr have restocked their supply of black powder.
'Thank you for destroying the black powder. You have thwarted what would have been a devastating attack.'
'Your mission is to infiltrate Eshadûr and destroy their new supply of black powder.'
Your mission is to infiltrate Eshadûr and destroy their new supply of black powder.\n\nTalk to Khâdamul when you are ready to begin.
